title: [Maelstrom Bay, Bottom]
description: To the west a coral reef grows out of the golden sand of the bay floor.  A large colony of spiral gilled tube worms has attached itself to the coral.  The wreck of a small coastal cutter lies on its side.  The tracks of crabs and lobsters lead in and out of the wreck.
paths: Obvious exits: north, northeast, east, southeast, south, up
